Preheat oven to 375 degrees F. Line shallow baking pan with aluminum foil; spray foil with cooking spray. Mix beef, tomato sauce, Egg Beaters, oats and soup mix in large bowl until well blended. Shape into 4 mini meatloaves, about 4x3 inches; place in prepared pan. Spread ketchup evenly over tops of meatloaves. Bake 25 minutes or until meatloaves are cooked through (160 degrees F). Let stand 5 minutes before serving.